== 争议 ==
2021年2月2-3日，LexBurner在bilibili直播时发表了与动画《[[无职转生～到了异世界就拿出真本事～|无职转生～到了异世界就拿出真本事～]]》相關的有所争议的言论<ref>{{cite web |title=He Was Bilibili’s Top Livestreamer. Then He Insulted Some Fans. |url=https://www.sixthtone.com/news/1006832/He%20Was%20Bilibili%E2%80%99s%20Top%20Livestreamer.%20Then%20He%20Insulted%20Some%20Fans. |website=Sixth Tone |accessdate=2021-02-10 |date=2021-02-10 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222032858/https://www.sixthtone.com/news/1006832/He%20Was%20Bilibili%E2%80%99s%20Top%20Livestreamer.%20Then%20He%20Insulted%20Some%20Fans. }}</ref>。2月4日，原作者[[不讲理不求人|不讲理不求人]]在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上回应相关争议。当天，LexBurner在[[新浪微博|新浪微博]]表示抱歉，并表示要“好好审视自己”<ref>{{cite web |author=LexBurner |title=非常抱歉给所有人带来了不愉快，需要好好审视自己。 |url=https://weibo.com/1893347753/K0iSde6n1?type=comment |via=新浪微博 |date=2021-02-04 |access-date=2021-02-17 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210208162106/https://weibo.com/1893347753/K0iSde6n1?type=comment |archivedate=2021-02-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月5日，LexBurner在bilibili发布动态对其部分言论表示抱歉并表示“我嘴臭、膨胀，但是请大家不要曲解我的意思”、“没有映射与攻击任何人”。<ref>{{cite web |title=LexBurner的动态-哔哩哔哩 |url=https://t.bilibili.com/488330535948685841?tab=2 |date=2021-02-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210215061639/https://t.bilibili.com/488330535948685841?tab=2 |archivedate=2021-02-15 |access-date=2021-02-15 }}</ref>

2021年2月7日，无职转生突然被在B站下架<ref>{{Cite web|title=动态-哔哩哔哩|url=https://t.bilibili.com/489059460624209518|accessdate=2021-02-09|author=哔哩哔哩番剧|date=2021-02-07|format=|work=t.bilibili.com|publisher=|language=|quote=因突发技术故障[…]|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210223048/https://t.bilibili.com/489059460624209518}}</ref>，B站旋即于於2月8日晚间宣布，因其在直播中多次发布争议言论，涉及引战、攻击他人，对用户和其他UP主不尊重，违反社区相关规则，将对签约主播LexBurner违反合约的行为起诉、追究[[法律责任|法律责任]]；得出司法结论前封禁LexBurner的账号及直播间；撤-{}-销其“bilibili 2020百大UP主”、“bilibili 2020年度杰出主播”荣誉；取消其参与“创作激励计划”及其他社区激励活动的资格<ref>{{cite web |title=B站处罚百万粉丝UP主LexBurner：封禁账号 起诉追究法律责任 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-02-09/doc-ikftpnny5920866.shtml |website=新浪科技 |accessdate=2021-02-09 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209041127/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-02-09/doc-ikftpnny5920866.shtml }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=B站起诉UP主LexBurner并封号，后者曾为直播言论致歉，涉事动漫下架 |url=http://tech.caijing.com.cn/20210209/4738478.shtml |website=财经网科技频道 |accessdate=2021-02-09 |date=2021-02-09 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213024806/http://tech.caijing.com.cn/20210209/4738478.shtml }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=bilibili Suspends Mushoku Tensei Streaming in China Due to 'Technical Failure'|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2021-02-10/bilibili-suspends-mushoku-tensei-streaming-in-china-due-to-technical-failure/.169340|accessdate=2021-02-13|work=Anime News Network|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614220100/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2021-02-10/bilibili-suspends-mushoku-tensei-streaming-in-china-due-to-technical-failure/.169340}}</ref><ref name="处罚公告">{{cite web |author1=哔哩哔哩弹幕网 |title=对UP主LexBurner违规以及违约行为的处罚公告 |url=https://t.bilibili.com/489440892375032127 |website=bilibili.com |accessdate=2021-02-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210210155515/https://t.bilibili.com/489440892375032127 |archivedate=2021-02-10 }}</ref>。

2021年12月9日，哔哩哔哩发布关于违约UP主LexBurner法律仲裁结论的公告，称Lex担负违约责任，分期赔偿哔哩哔哩人民币2000万元。另外Lex称希望委托哔哩哔哩向动画学院捐赠人民币200万元。与此同时，LexBurnner获得解封，Lex表示接受裁决，履行责任<ref>{{cite web |title=关于违约UP主LexBurner法律仲裁结论的公告 |url=https://t.bilibili.com/602188697334024380?tab=2 |website=哔哩哔哩 |accessdate=2021-12-09 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210210155515/https://t.bilibili.com/489440892375032127 |archivedate=2021-02-10 }}</ref>。

